snippet: Frida Hansdotter of Sweden dominated a World Cup night slalom in Flachau. Tina Maze of Slovenia was 0.61 of a second behind in second, and the American Mikaela Shiffrin was third.
abstract: Frida Hansdotter dominates World Cup slalom event at Flachau, Austria.
lead_paragraph: Frida Hansdotter of Sweden dominated a World Cup night slalom in Flachau. Tina Maze of Slovenia was 0.61 of a second behind in second, and the American Mikaela Shiffrin was third.

headline.main: Swede Wins Night Slalom in Austria
headline.print_headline: Swede Wins World Cup Night Slalom
